snippet.title: Kiko and the Game Kids: Baseball Bash - Official Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Music by the lovely "What's Shakin, Bakon?"
Give him a follow! https://soundcloud.com/bakonbakon

A baseball game? Of all things?
That is NOT what I expected to come out after Super-Heroes and Monsters but ok I guess? Help Kiko, Beamy and Ash escape a baseball themed trap created by X and his super-villan buddies!

Get ready to bash some baseballs!
